\c 14
\p
\v 1 Mukadzi umwe neumwe wakachenjera anovaka imba yake; asi mukadzi benzi anoiputsa nemaoko ake.
\p
\v 2 Anofamba mukururama kwake anotya Jehovha; asi wakatsauka panzira dzake anomuzvidza.
\p
\v 3 Mumuromo mebenzi mune shamhu yekuzvikudza; asi miromo yevakachenjera inovachengetedza.
\p
\v 4 Pasina dzinzombe chidyiro chakachena; asi kune goho guru nesimba renzombe.
\p
\v 5 Chapupu chakatendeka kwazvo hachirevi nhema zhinji; asi chapupu chenhema chinofema nhema zhinji.
\p
\v 6 Mutuki anotsvaka uchenjeri, asi ha\add hu\add*po; asi ruzivo rwakareruka kune anonzwisisa.
\p
\v 7 Ibva pamberi pemunhu benzi, kana usingaongorori \add kwaari\add* miromo yeruzivo.
\p
\v 8 Uchenjeri hweakangwara kunzwisisa nzira yake; asi upenzi hwemapenzi unyengeri.
\p
\v 9 Mapenzi anoseka pachivi; asi pakati pevakarurama pane nyasha.
\p
\v 10 Moyo unoziva kurwadziwa kwawo pachawo; uye mweni haangagoverani nemufaro wawo.
\p
\v 11 Imba yewakaipa ichaparadzwa; asi tende rewakarurama richatunga.
\p
\v 12 Pane nzira yakarurama mukuona kwemunhu; asi kuguma kwayo inzira dzerufu.
\p
\v 13 Kunyange pakuseka moyo uri mumarwadzo; uye kuguma kwemufaro \add uyu\add* kushungurudzika.
\p
\v 14 Anodzokera shure pamoyo achaguta kubva panzira dzake, asi munhu wakanaka kubva pachake.
\p
\v 15 Asina ruzivo anotenda shoko rimwe nerimwe; asi wakachenjera anongwarira nhanho yake.
\p
\v 16 Wakachenjera anotya uye anobva pane zvakaipa; asi benzi rinotsamwa uye richi\add zvi\add*vimba.
\p
\v 17 Anokurumidza kutsamwa anoita neupenzi; uye munhu wemazano akaipa anovengwa.
\p
\v 18 Vasina ruzivo vanogara nhaka yeupenzi; asi vakangwara vanodzikwa korona yeruzivo.
\p
\v 19 Vakaipa vanokotama pamberi pevakanaka, nevakashata pamasuwo ewakarurama.
\p
\v 20 Murombo anovengwa kunyange newekwake; asi vanoda wakafuma vazhinji.
\p
\v 21 Anozvidza wekwake anotadza; asi ane tsitsi kuvarombo wakaropafadzwa.
\p
\v 22 Vanoronga zvakaipa havatadzi here? Asi nyasha nechokwadi \add ndezve\add*vanoronga zvakanaka.
\p
\v 23 Pakushingaira kose pane mubairo; asi shoko remiromo rinounza kushaiwa chete.
\p
\v 24 Korona yevakachenjera ifuma yavo; upenzi hwemapenzi upenzi.
\p
\v 25 Chapupu chechokwadi chinonunura mweya; asi anofema nhema munyengeri.
\p
\v 26 Pakutya Jehovha pane chivimbo chakasimba; uye vana vake vachava neutiziro.
\p
\v 27 Kutya Jehovha chitubu cheupenyu, kutendeuka kubva pamisungo yerufu.
\p
\v 28 Kushonga kwamambo kuri pakuwanda kwevanhu; asi kuparadzwa kwemutongi kuri pakushaikwa kwevanhu.
\p
\v 29 Anononoka kutsamwa ndewekunzwisisa kukuru; asi ane mweya mupfupi anokurisa upenzi.
\p
\v 30 Moyo wakagwinya upenyu hwenyama; asi godo kuora kwemapfupa.
\p
\v 31 Mumanikidzi wemurombo anotuka Muiti wake; asi ane tsitsi kune anoshaiwa anomukudza.
\p
\v 32 Wakaipa anowisirwa pasi muzvakaipa zvake; asi wakarurama ane tariro pakufa kwake.
\p
\v 33 Uchenjeri hunogara pamoyo weanonzwisisa; asi zviri mukati memapenzi zvinozikanwa.
\p
\v 34 Kururama kunokwiridzira rudzi; asi chivi chinyangadzo kuvanhu.
\p
\v 35 Nyasha dzamambo dziri pamuranda wakachenjera; asi hasha dzake dzichava \add pane\add* anonyadzisa.
